------------------------------------------------------------------------
all 64-bit architectures
------------------------------------------------------------------------

  test cases rsp_lrso, rsp_lrso2, rsp_phosph, rsp_socorr and
  rsp_sreslrso will not work if Dalton is compiled as 64-bit code


------------------------------------------------------------------------
SGI 64-bit
------------------------------------------------------------------------

  On some (all?) SGIs the test case energy_solv does not work
  when compiling the 64-bit version (32-bit works fine)


------------------------------------------------------------------------
DEC alpha
------------------------------------------------------------------------

  due to problems in ERI the following test cases do not work correctly:

	cc_energy_triplesdirect		
	cc_energy_triplesdirect2	
	cc_energy_triplesdirect3	
				
  Also, the following geometry optimization tests fail:

        walk_gradex
        walk_image
        walk_modeflw

  Some of the tests appear to be sensitive to the compilation flags but
  give expected results when dalton is compiled with the default flags:
  walk_vibave, geoopt_symbrk, prop_nucquad, rsp_esr, rsp_mnfphosph
  and geoopt_prop3


------------------------------------------------------------------------
SUN
------------------------------------------------------------------------

  test case cc_energy_field does not work because certain I/O routines
  have not been implemented for this platform yet
